column2: select top # s.zwarning, w.w3mag, e.zerr, e.z, xm.sdss_objid, s.bestObjID, s.specObjID, e.specObjID from wise_xmatch as xm join SpecObjAll as s on xm.sdss_objid = s.bestObjID join emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID join wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr where e.z> # and e.zerr/e.z< =#
